objective_measured.note: optimizer_objective is used to guide parameter updates; best_sample_energy is the lowest QUBO energy from any single bitstring; post_processed_objective is after local-swap repair

feasibility_policy.repair_description: After optimization, the best raw bitstring is taken. A single round of local bit-flip swap is applied: each variable is flipped and the resulting QUBO energy is checked. If any flip improves the objective, the best flip is kept.

transpiler_settings.note: transpiled circuit metrics available per-job in job_metadata
